{"word":"ὁμολογουμένως","slug":"ὁμολογουμένως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁμολογουμένως</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>adverb from <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> of <a href='S:ὁμολογέω'><el>ὁμολογέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>conformably with</i>, <el>τοῖς εἰρημένοις</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>by common consent, confessedly</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}